             sworn. - The prisoner was brought to our office in custody; he had this blue apron and steel on, and a blue jacket; he broke the cieling of the lock-up house, and would have escaped if I had not come as I did.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's defence. The young woman is mistaken in the person. <rs id="t18030112-28-verdict155" type="verdictDescription">
